{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2015, "height": 2767, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [127, 1037, 201, 1431], "block_id": 0, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "四一七", "block_bbox": [135, 2080, 190, 2204], "block_id": 1, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "第二章受姓本祖", "block_bbox": [304, 243, 627, 298], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "1.受姓祖先杜泄2.杜赫由郢迁南阳日3.中原杜姓迁茂陵第三章杜姓流布（分25部分，分列全国及海外的杜姓）", "block_bbox": [300, 311, 1485, 431], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "第四章杜姓盛事", "block_bbox": [302, 441, 625, 494], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "1.邺郡杜皇后家族2.魏郡杜皇后家族3.世代高官杜铨家族4.皇后与宰相世家5.建康的杜坦家族6.唐宰相杜佑家族7.义兴公杜杲家族8.巩县杜审言家族9.濮州的宰相世家10.宰相杜正伦家族11.定州杜太后家族12.名将杜桐大家族", "block_bbox": [438, 506, 1568, 757], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "第五章杜姓文化\n1.杜姓人的文学作品2.杜姓人的史学作品\n3.杜姓人的科学作品4.杜姓人家的族谱", "block_bbox": [303, 773, 1224, 957], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "第六章杜姓名人（列39人，从略）", "block_bbox": [302, 968, 963, 1022], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "第七章杜姓胜迹", "block_bbox": [302, 1032, 626, 1085], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "1.杜公祠2.杜甫故里3.杜甫草堂4.杜甫墓5.杜文秀墓", "block_bbox": [444, 1098, 1550, 1148], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "有关杜姓诗歌二首", "block_bbox": [757, 1226, 1341, 1307], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜家风范", "block_bbox": [387, 1399, 569, 1449], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "周时尧裔迁杜国，杜陵遗迹在诉说。杜康酿酒传说早，杜诗称母有字托。杜笃文采涉足广，杜预武库百科作。伏威起义惩贪官，如晦良相善定夺。审言文章并四友，杜甫诗圣耀祖国。杜佑通典二百卷，辟出史界新境廓。杜牧晚唐善绝句，齐名商隐并肩坐。杜祸未然人君事，防微杜渐占高着。", "block_bbox": [385, 1464, 1084, 1966], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：据《通志·氏族略》记载，周成王时，把原唐国的国君，尧的后裔迁往杜国，称为杜伯。现在陕西西安市东南留有杜陵的遗迹，在诉说着这段历史。杜字，从木从土。木作栏杆土筑墙，木土结合堵祸殃。居安思危，防微杜渐是君子的德相。能杜祸于未然者，乃君子矣。（摘自《新编百家姓》)", "block_bbox": [300, 1978, 1799, 2227], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏家谱", "block_bbox": [392, 2242, 571, 2290], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "安徽池州庞固（水渍）在这古老的事物中我领有我的一席之地。", "block_bbox": [390, 2308, 826, 2488], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 14}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9282900094985962, "coordinate": [300.64324951171875, 1978.5225830078125, 1799.787841796875, 2227.12890625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9066033959388733, "coordinate": [385.61395263671875, 1464.0379638671875, 1084.62353515625, 1966.2896728515625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7398908138275146, "coordinate": [390.15936279296875, 2308.29931640625, 826.5217895507812, 2488.03173828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7208443284034729, "coordinate": [438.53436279296875, 506.80987548828125, 1568.883544921875, 757.7238159179688]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.6888295412063599, "coordinate": [387.31878662109375, 1399.865966796875, 569.1548461914062, 1449.37646484375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.6753291487693787, "coordinate": [304.251708984375, 243.2966766357422, 627.064453125, 298.21026611328125]}, 